\begin{frame}{Outline}
  \begin{columns}
    \begin{column}{.5\textwidth}
      \begin{itemize}
      \item A Higgs-like boson was discovered in 2012 at the LHC.
      \item How did we decide we'd discovered something?
      \item How do we answer the question: ``Is it the Higgs?''
      \end{itemize}
